## Editor & Formatting
- [TOOL-01] **MUST** provide `.editorconfig`; enforce Prettier for formatting.

## Lint & Types
- [TOOL-02] **MUST** configure ESLint + TypeScript strict mode (no implicit any, strict null checks).
- [TOOL-03] **SHOULD** enable import/order and naming-convention rules aligned with `CODE-*`.

## Commits & Security
- [TOOL-04] **MUST** use Commitlint for Conventional Commits.
- [TOOL-05] **MUST** enable Dependabot/Snyk (deps); enable Gitleaks/TruffleHog (secret scanning).

## CI Integration
- [TOOL-06] **MUST** fail pipeline on lint/type/test/security scan errors.
- [TOOL-07] **SHOULD** publish SBOM and signed artifacts in releases.
